<h2 id="orgc355449">Use pseudo code to keep track of what you do</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orgc355449">
<p>
When you write docstrings use pseudo code to document the logical
structure
</p>

<pre class="example">
for ec in len(dict_levenshtein):
    for path in ec:
	for question in path:
	   do x
	for answer in path:
	   do y
</pre>
</div>
</div>
